  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">DEC 2020 Coronavirus Appeal Phase 1- Hajjah Governorate</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project scope is focused on protect IDPs and most vulnerable host communities from public health risks of COVID -19 pandemic, through improved access to and knowledge of water, sanitation and positive hygiene behaviours. It will complement existing WASH activities with a strengthened focus on COVID -19 prevention and response to ensure safe access to safe water and promotion of sanitation and hygiene. The proposed intervention under this project will be implemented by Oxfam in Hajjah. Oxfam Yemen COVID -19 response plan is to contribute to the control of the pandemic and to mitigate against its impact; and reducing risk of transmission a within communities, especially for the most vulnerable and displaced people.</narrative>
  </description>
